<br>
Okay... so I knew i was going to die... <br>
I'm not some sort of idiot who wraps his head in cotton wool and thinks to himslef.. <br>
&quot;Nothing can hurt me.. tra la la!&quot; <br>
That aint me... <br>
But my GOOD GOD! <br>
I spent all day and most of the night getting back on my feet. <br>
Bully for all you peeps who have been playing years and can get to Sorcerer in one reset but it takes me signifigantly longer. <br>
The last little while i have made Hero/Super a couple of times and not been able to go that extra mile.. <br>
