At which point.. THIS PLEA comes ringing out like a Bell in the misty evening air... <br>
<br>
*A female voice in the distance shouts &quot;Is there anyone that just wants to <br>
play instead of kill kill kill?&quot;. <br>
<br>
So i say yes.. thats fine.. sorry about him he's unstable, <br>
La la la etc.. <br>
<br>
