And lo and behold... <br>
<br>
ZZZzzz... <br>
*You have just been woken up! <br>
Your stamina is 41. <br>
You are winded by the violence of a masterly lunge by someone. <br>
Stamina=0... <br>
You feel your lifeblood halting... <br>
You have been killed by someone. <br>
Sack0 dropped. <br>
Unlit brand40 dropped. <br>
Coal dropped. <br>
Fork1 dropped. <br>
Key1 dropped. <br>
Net dropped. <br>
Not updating persona. <br>
<br>
Now... <br>
How do u think i felt at this point... its 4.30 am... nobody else was on but me and Thwomp.. so it was the same anti Pker that snuck up on me and hit me for 40 dmg.. <br>
WHILE I WAS SLEEPING... <br>
AFTER COMPLAINING ABOUT PKers. <br>
<br>
Now yes i should have been more careful... <br>
Perhaps i did not expect a BLATANT LIE from the other party regarding their stance on PKing as i happen to be quite a trusting person. <br>
I see now that having trust in this game is something that is useless. <br>
They were a Warlock... to hit a Sorcerer... a NEWBIE sorcerer while on low health, while asleep, while you are invisible, after STATING that u were not interested in Pking. <br>
Alright i should have seen it coming but GOD DAMN IT! <br>
<br>
My point in all this... is that the PKing in this game is based on opportunism for the greater part... <br>
